#: ../../source/reference/tensor/generated/maxframe.tensor.average.rst:2
msgid "maxframe.tensor.average"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.tensor.statistics.average.average:1 of
msgid "Compute the weighted average along the specified axis."
msgstr "沿指定轴计算加权平均值。"

#: maxframe.tensor.statistics.average.average of
msgid "参数"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.tensor.statistics.average.average:3 of
msgid ""
"Tensor containing data to be averaged. If `a` is not a tensor, a "
"conversion is attempted."
msgstr "包含要求平均值的数据的张量。如果 `a` 不是张量，则尝试进行转换。"

#: maxframe.tensor.statistics.average.average:6 of
msgid ""
"Axis or axes along which to average `a`.  The default, axis=None, will "
"average over all of the elements of the input tensor. If axis is negative"
" it counts from the last to the first axis.  If axis is a tuple of ints, "
"averaging is performed on all of the axes specified in the tuple instead "
"of a single axis or all the axes as before."
msgstr ""
"沿指定轴或轴集对 `a` 求平均值。默认值 axis=None 表示对输入张量的所有元素"
"求平均值。如果 axis 为负数，则从最后一个轴向第一个轴计数。如果 axis 是"
"整数元组，则在元组中指定的所有轴上进行平均，而不是像以前那样在单个轴或"
"所有轴上进行。"

#: maxframe.tensor.statistics.average.average:6 of
msgid ""
"Axis or axes along which to average `a`.  The default, axis=None, will "
"average over all of the elements of the input tensor. If axis is negative"
" it counts from the last to the first axis."
msgstr ""
"用于对 `a` 进行平均的轴。默认情况下，axis=None 将对输入张量的所有元素进行"
"平均。如果 axis 为负数，则从最后一个轴向前计数。"

#: maxframe.tensor.statistics.average.average:10 of
msgid ""
"If axis is a tuple of ints, averaging is performed on all of the axes "
"specified in the tuple instead of a single axis or all the axes as "
"before."
msgstr ""
"如果 axis 是一个整数元组，则对元组中指定的所有轴执行平均，而不是像之前"
"那样对单个轴或所有轴进行平均。"

#: maxframe.tensor.statistics.average.average:14 of
msgid ""
"A tensor of weights associated with the values in `a`. Each value in `a` "
"contributes to the average according to its associated weight. The "
"weights tensor can either be 1-D (in which case its length must be the "
"size of `a` along the given axis) or of the same shape as `a`. If "
"`weights=None`, then all data in `a` are assumed to have a weight equal "
"to one."
msgstr ""
"与 `a` 中值相关联的权重张量。`a` 中的每个值根据其关联的权重对平均值产生"
"贡献。权重张量可以是一维的（在这种情况下，其长度必须等于 `a` 在给定轴上的"
"大小），也可以与 `a` 具有相同的形状。如果 `weights=None`，则假定 `a` 中的"
"所有数据都具有相等的权重，即一。"

#: maxframe.tensor.statistics.average.average:21 of
msgid ""
"Default is `False`. If `True`, the tuple (`average`, `sum_of_weights`) is"
" returned, otherwise only the average is returned. If `weights=None`, "
"`sum_of_weights` is equivalent to the number of elements over which the "
"average is taken."
msgstr ""
"默认值为 `False`。如果为 `True`，则返回元组 (`average`, `sum_of_weights`)"
"，否则仅返回平均值。如果 `weights=None`，则 `sum_of_weights` 等效于计算"
"平均值时所涉及的元素数量。"

#: maxframe.tensor.statistics.average.average of
msgid "返回"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.tensor.statistics.average.average:27 of
msgid ""
"**average, [sum_of_weights]** -- Return the average along the specified "
"axis. When returned is `True`, return a tuple with the average as the "
"first element and the sum of the weights as the second element. The "
"return type is `Float` if `a` is of integer type, otherwise it is of the "
"same type as `a`. `sum_of_weights` is of the same type as `average`."
msgstr ""
"**average, [sum_of_weights]** -- 返回沿指定轴的平均值。当 returned 为 `"
"True` 时，返回一个元组，其中平均值为第一个元素，权重之和为第二个元素。"
"如果 `a` 是整数类型，则返回类型是 `Float`，否则与 `a` 类型相同。`sum_of_"
"weights` 与 `average` 的类型相同。"

#: maxframe.tensor.statistics.average.average of
msgid "返回类型"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.tensor.statistics.average.average of
msgid "抛出"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.tensor.statistics.average.average:34 of
msgid ""
"When all weights along axis are zero. See `numpy.ma.average` for a     "
"version robust to this type of error."
msgstr ""
"当沿轴的所有权重都为零时。有关对此类错误具有鲁棒性的版本，请参见 `numpy."
"ma.average`。"

#: maxframe.tensor.statistics.average.average:35 of
msgid ""
"When the length of 1D `weights` is not the same as the shape of `a`     "
"along axis."
msgstr "当一维 `weights` 的长度与 `a` 沿轴的形状不一致时。"

#: maxframe.tensor.statistics.average.average:37 of
msgid ":py:obj:`mean`"
msgstr ""

